   | struct typeId < typeParameterIR* > { fieldTypeIR* } (from structTypeDefIR)
   | header typeId < typeParameterIR* > { fieldTypeIR* } (from headerTypeDefIR)
   | header_union typeId < typeParameterIR* > { fieldTypeIR* } (from headerUnionTypeDefIR)
   | enum typeId { nameIR* } (from simpleEnumTypeIR) hint(print %0)
   | enum typeId < typeIR > { valueFieldIR* } (from serializableEnumTypeIR) hint(print %0)
   | extern typeId < typeParameterIR* , typeParameterIR* > externMethodTypeDefEnv (from externObjectTypeDefIR)
   | parser typeId < typeParameterIR* , typeParameterIR* > ( parameterIR* ) (from parserObjectTypeDefIR)
   | control typeId < typeParameterIR* , typeParameterIR* > ( parameterIR* ) (from controlObjectTypeDefIR)
   | package typeId < typeParameterIR* , typeParameterIR* > { typeIR* } (from packageObjectTypeDefIR)
   | table typeId { tableMetadataStructTypeIR } (from tableObjectTypeIR) hint(print %0)

